{"tid":386902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬路邊企住生B 花裙女生完就閃","createTime":"2017-09-04T08:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T08:59:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c735dece382cc4609f744da2904aebbc77a690d","tid":386902,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:51:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20142479&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20142479%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170904&d=2O%2FuI0XC9AMasLbiUOLmrEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=303cb738\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20142479%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170904&h=bbaa7136\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20142479&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170904</a><br />\n<br />\n馬路邊企住生B<br />\n花裙女生完就閃<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真正的呱呱墮地！廣東雲浮前日上演驚人一幕，一名穿着吊帶花裙孕婦在路上行走時，突然作動當街分娩。她站在路上，初生嬰兒、羊水撒滿一地，周圍途人都嚇得驚呆了。隨後，醫護人員接報趕來救助兩母子，為其剪臍帶等善後工作。豈料，女子立即從擔架起身，抱着初生嬰兒提着菜離開。<br />\n<br />\n有網民事後發帖透露：「今天早上這位有點精神障礙的阿姨在街上生子的事情，朋友能不能幫忙找找她的家人？她和孩子在中醫院，都不讓人靠近，BB出生頭下地加幾小時沒有進食，麻煩客位幫忙找找她家人。」<br />\n<br />\n梨視頻/新浪微博"},{"pid":"994e759a4ab6ab742d89b534892fc5a87cdf9950","tid":386902,"uid":118547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"個閪要有幾闊先可以生仔冇感覺 行行下跌出黎又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}